 Ye Ji unexpectedly suffered convulsions and lost consciousness, leading to her collapse.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emergency services were promptly called, and CPR was administered at the scene.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cardiopulmonary_resuscitation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3367243332770546e-12, \"text\": \"CPR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cardiopulmonary_resuscitation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cardiopulmonary_resuscitation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately, Kim Ye Ji\\u00a0regained consciousness within 10 minutes.An official from Imsil County reported that Kim's condition is being closely monitored at the hospital.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imsil_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imsil County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imsil_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imsil_County\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9995993616407608, \"rank\": 0.0003803681956786428, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\